<lb n="0869b10" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 145 [Nos. 125(52.1), 144]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0869b11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>佛母般泥洹經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0869b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0869b13" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0869011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（劉）＋宋【元】【明】</note><note n="0869011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宋【大】，劉宋【元】【明】</note><app n="0869011"><lem wit="【大】">宋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">劉宋</rdg></app>沙門<note n="0869012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（釋）＋慧【三】</note><note n="0869012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慧【大】，釋慧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869012"><lem wit="【大】">慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">釋慧</rdg></app>簡譯</byline>
<lb n="0869b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0869b1401">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869b1404" rend="inline">一時，佛在維耶<note n="0869013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離＝梨【三】＊</note><note n="0869013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">離【大】＊，梨【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869013"><lem wit="【大】">離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">梨</rdg></app>國，行在獼猴水邊
<lb n="0869b15" ed="T"/>拘羅曷講堂上。大愛道比丘尼者，即<note n="0869014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從佛＝佛姨【三】</note><note n="0869014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從佛【大】，佛姨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869014"><lem wit="【大】">從佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">佛姨</rdg></app>母
<lb n="0869b16" ed="T"/>也，時在維耶<app type="star" corresp="#0869013"><lem wit="【大】">離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">梨</rdg></app>國，與<note n="0869015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女除饉＝除饉女【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0869015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女除饉【大】＊，除饉女【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0869015"><lem wit="【大】">女除饉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">除饉女</rdg></app>五百人俱，皆
<lb n="0869b17" ed="T"/>是應真，獲六通四達神足變化，年<note n="0869016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耆＝長【三】</note><note n="0869016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆【大】，長【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869016"><lem wit="【大】">耆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">長</rdg></app>德尊神
<lb n="0869b18" ed="T"/><note n="0869017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曜＝燿【三】＊</note><note n="0869017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曜【大】＊，燿【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869017"><lem wit="【大】">曜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">燿</rdg></app>巍巍，其精舍在王園，所度無量，深入普智
<lb n="0869b19" ed="T"/>定，覩世尊逮阿難、<note n="0869018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鶖鷺＝秋露【宋】＊</note><note n="0869018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鶖鷺【大】＊，秋露【宋】＊</note><app n="0869018"><lem wit="【大】">鶖鷺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">秋露</rdg></app>子、大目<note n="0869019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乾〕－【三】</note><note n="0869019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869019"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>連，所度
<lb n="0869b20" ed="T"/>已畢將欲滅度日，「吾不忍見世尊、如來、無所
<lb n="0869b21" ed="T"/>著、正真道、最正覺，及諸應真<note n="0869020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔泥曰〕－【三】</note><note n="0869020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥曰【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869020"><lem wit="【大】">泥曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，吾當先息
<lb n="0869b22" ed="T"/>靈還<note n="0869021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝于【三】</note><note n="0869021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎【大】＊，于【宋】【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0869021"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">于</rdg></app>本無矣。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869b2207" rend="inline">佛一切智具照其然，即告阿
<lb n="0869b23" ed="T"/>難：「大愛道念曰：『吾不忍見世尊，并諸應真泥
<lb n="0869b24" ed="T"/><note n="0869022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝洹【三】＊</note><note n="0869022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】＊，洹【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869022"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洹</rdg></app>，欲先滅度。』」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869b2406" rend="inline">阿難聞教即稽首言：「今聞尊
<lb n="0869b25" ed="T"/>命，四體萎墮心塞智索，不識四方之名。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869b2516" rend="inline">佛告
<lb n="0869b26" ed="T"/>阿難：「汝謂大愛道滅度，將戒種、慧種、<note n="0869023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔定種〕－【三】</note><note n="0869023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">定種【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869023"><lem wit="【大】">定種</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、解
<lb n="0869b27" ed="T"/>脫種、度知見種，<note n="0869024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【三】</note><note n="0869024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869024"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四意止、四意斷、四神足、五
<lb n="0869b28" ed="T"/>根、五力、七覺意、八<note n="0869025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔品〕－【三】</note><note n="0869025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">品【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869025"><lem wit="【大】">品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>道行去耶？」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869b2813" rend="inline">對曰：「不也。
<lb n="0869b29" ed="T"/>但惟佛生七日<note n="0869026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【三】</note><note n="0869026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，太【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869026"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">太</rdg></app>后薨，母慈至有<note n="0869027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0869027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869027"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弘恩
<pb n="0869c" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0145.0869c"/>
<lb n="0869c01" ed="T"/>在佛所耳。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869c0105" rend="inline">世尊歎曰：「真如汝言，母於吾誠有
<lb n="0869c02" ed="T"/>哺乳重恩之惠，吾亦有難算之恩在母所也。
<lb n="0869c03" ed="T"/><note n="0869028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【宋】</note><note n="0869028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由【大】，猶【宋】</note><app n="0869028"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">猶</rdg></app>吾明獲歸命佛、歸命法、歸命聖眾，自歸
<lb n="0869c04" ed="T"/><note n="0869029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0869029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習【大】＊，集【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0869029"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app><note n="0869030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡道＝道盡【三】＊</note><note n="0869030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡道【大】＊，道盡【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869030"><lem wit="【大】">盡道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">道盡</rdg></app>冥滅明盛，無疑於三尊，苦<app type="star" corresp="#0869029"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡道
<lb n="0869c05" ed="T"/>道眼明盡解，結解獲無所著。若人能<note n="0869031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悟＝寤【宋】</note><note n="0869031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悟【大】，寤【宋】</note><app n="0869031"><lem wit="【大】">悟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">寤</rdg></app>愚者
<lb n="0869c06" ed="T"/>之惑，令入<note n="0869032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正真＝真正【三】＊</note><note n="0869032" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->正真【大】＊，真正【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869032"><lem wit="【大】">正真</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">真正</rdg></app>，歸佛、歸法、歸<app type="star" corresp="#0869021"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">于</rdg></app>聖眾，自歸
<lb n="0869c07" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0869029"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0869030"><lem wit="【大】">盡道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">道盡</rdg></app>者，受道弟子，盡天下名珍，訖其年
<lb n="0869c08" ed="T"/>壽供養經師，萬未<note n="0869033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塞＝賽【元】【明】</note><note n="0869033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塞【大】，賽【元】【明】</note><app n="0869033"><lem wit="【大】">塞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">賽</rdg></app>一，歸命三尊恩過須
<lb n="0869c09" ed="T"/>彌，弟子<note n="0869034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【元】【明】</note><note n="0869034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由【大】，猶【元】【明】</note><app n="0869034"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>芥子也。是故，阿難！吾有重恩於
<lb n="0869c10" ed="T"/>大愛道<note n="0869035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所〕－【宋】</note><note n="0869035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0869035"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，其為無量<note n="0869036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝矣【三】</note><note n="0869036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也【大】，矣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869036"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">矣</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869c1010" rend="inline"><note n="0869037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於時〕－【宋】</note><note n="0869037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於時【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0869037"><lem wit="【大】">於時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大愛道與除
<lb n="0869c11" ed="T"/>饉女五百人俱到佛所，<note n="0869038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】</note><note n="0869038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869038"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭面著<note n="0869039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】</note><note n="0869039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869039"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>足退
<lb n="0869c12" ed="T"/>叉手立。大愛道白佛言：「吾不忍覩佛及諸應
<lb n="0869c13" ed="T"/>真滅度，欲先泥<app type="star" corresp="#0869022"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洹</rdg></app>。」佛默可之。大愛道以手
<lb n="0869c14" ed="T"/>摩佛足曰：「吾免覩如來、應儀、正真道、最正覺、
<lb n="0869c15" ed="T"/>道法御、天人師、三界明，自今不復覩之矣。」五
<lb n="0869c16" ed="T"/>百除饉女陳辭如上，佛亦可之也，為說身患
<lb n="0869c17" ed="T"/>生死憂悲苦、不如意<note n="0869040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𤺙＝惱【三】＊</note><note n="0869040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤺙【大】＊，惱【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869040"><lem wit="【大】">𤺙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惱</rdg></app><note n="0869041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之難〕－【宋】</note><note n="0869041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之難【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0869041"><lem wit="【大】">之難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，<note n="0869042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（又嘆）＋無【三】</note><note n="0869042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，又嘆無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869042"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">又嘆無</rdg></app>欲清淨空
<lb n="0869c18" ed="T"/>不願無<note n="0869043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝想【三】＊</note><note n="0869043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】＊，想【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869043"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">想</rdg></app>滅度之安若干淨品。諸女除饉莫
<lb n="0869c19" ed="T"/>不歡喜，繞佛三匝稽首而去。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0869c1912" rend="inline">還<note n="0869044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝于【宋】【元】，於【明】</note><note n="0869044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎【大】，于【宋】【元】，於【明】</note><app n="0869044"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">于</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">於</rdg></app>精舍，布五
<lb n="0869c20" ed="T"/>百座，皆各就<note n="0869045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【三】＊</note><note n="0869045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐【大】＊，座【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869045"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">座</rdg></app>。大愛道現神足德，自<app type="star" corresp="#0869045"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">座</rdg></app>沒
<lb n="0869c21" ed="T"/>地從東方來，在虛空中化，去地一樹轉昇<note n="0869046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（至）＋七【三】</note><note n="0869046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，至七【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869046"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">至七</rdg></app>
<lb n="0869c22" ed="T"/>樹，經行虛空中，乍坐乍臥，上身出水，下身出
<lb n="0869c23" ed="T"/>火，下身出水，上身出火，又沒地中<note n="0869047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飛東＝飛從西【三】＊</note><note n="0869047" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->飛東【大】＊，飛從西【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0869047"><lem wit="【大】">飛東</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">飛從西</rdg></app>方
<lb n="0869c24" ed="T"/>來，沒法如前，八方上下來，放大光明以照諸
<lb n="0869c25" ed="T"/>冥中人，上<app type="star" corresp="#0869017"><lem wit="【大】">曜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">燿</rdg></app>諸天。五百除饉變化俱然，同時
<lb n="0869c26" ed="T"/>泥<app type="star" corresp="#0869022"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洹</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0869c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0869c2701">佛告賢者阿難：「汝明旦入城到耶游理家所，
<lb n="0869c28" ed="T"/>告之曰：『佛母及五百耆年除饉皆<note n="0869048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝如【明】</note><note n="0869048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，如【明】</note><app n="0869048"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">如</rdg></app>滅度，
<lb n="0869c29" ed="T"/>佛勸理家作五百輿床，麻油、香花、樟柟梓<note n="0869049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＝木【三】</note><note n="0869049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事【大】，木【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0869049"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">木</rdg></app>
<pb n="0870a" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0145.0870a"/>
<lb n="0870a01" ed="T"/>各五百，貢妓正音當以供養。所以然者？斯諸
<lb n="0870a02" ed="T"/>除饉皆六通四達，獲空不願無<app type="star" corresp="#0869043"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">想</rdg></app>淨定，今得
<lb n="0870a03" ed="T"/>泥<app type="star" corresp="#0869022"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洹</rdg></app>，為諸佛所歎，一時之供養，其福無數。』」阿
<lb n="0870a04" ed="T"/>難稽首于地惻然敬諾，平旦入城至理家門，
<lb n="0870a05" ed="T"/>告守門者曰：「入云吾來。」門人入，如事云。理家
<lb n="0870a06" ed="T"/>時在高觀與樂人相娛，聞阿難來，心怖毛<note n="0870001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竪＝豎【明】</note><note n="0870001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竪【大】，豎【明】</note><app n="0870001"><lem wit="【大】">竪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">豎</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0870a07" ed="T"/>即下觀疾出，五體投地，以<note n="0870002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手＝首【三】</note><note n="0870002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，首【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870002"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">首</rdg></app>著足長跪而曰：
<lb n="0870a08" ed="T"/>「賢者
<lb n="0870a09" ed="T"/>阿難！今來甚早，斯事非恒，將以何故？」阿難如
<lb n="0870a10" ed="T"/>佛教具為理家說之。理家聞之即<note n="0870003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擗＝躃【三】</note><note n="0870003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擗【大】＊，躃【宋】【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0870003"><lem wit="【大】">擗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">躃</rdg></app>身于地，
<lb n="0870a11" ed="T"/>抗哀而云：「吾等豈有非佛弟子不肖之行，而
<lb n="0870a12" ed="T"/>為除饉所棄矣，長逝無為而無遺教乎！」噓唏
<lb n="0870a13" ed="T"/>重曰：「賢者阿難！<note n="0870004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＋（今）【三】</note><note n="0870004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，自今【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870004"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">自今</rdg></app>維耶梨精舍都為空寂，王
<lb n="0870a14" ed="T"/>道四街不復覩神通女除饉，如彼<note n="0870005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛＝威【元】【明】</note><note n="0870005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盛【大】，威【元】【明】</note><app n="0870005"><lem wit="【大】">盛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">威</rdg></app>德行于
<lb n="0870a15" ed="T"/>國道。國道為空，其痛何甚乎！」阿難答曰：「佛說
<lb n="0870a16" ed="T"/>乾坤雖為長久，始必有終，盛者有衰，恩愛當
<lb n="0870a17" ed="T"/>離，覩異欲<note n="0870006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">永＝乖【三】</note><note n="0870006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">永【大】，乖【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870006"><lem wit="【大】">永</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">乖</rdg></app>者尋行受報，三界無常其如幻
<lb n="0870a18" ed="T"/>夢，古來非常苦身之患其禍無量，而愚者不
<lb n="0870a19" ed="T"/>見，可謂瞽矣。生求不死、會<note n="0870007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畢＝冀【三】</note><note n="0870007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畢【大】，冀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870007"><lem wit="【大】">畢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">冀</rdg></app>不離者，終不可
<lb n="0870a20" ed="T"/>得也、上賢覩佛經奧、解四非常，如盲得視，精
<lb n="0870a21" ed="T"/>進勤行可免重苦矣。」阿難引若干要說，以釋
<lb n="0870a22" ed="T"/>理家結，理家心解即喜。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0870a2210" rend="inline">阿難復至諸梵志理
<lb n="0870a23" ed="T"/>家所，時，其眾在講堂有異議，即告之曰：「佛勸
<lb n="0870a24" ed="T"/>諸賢者作五百人葬具。所以然者？佛母并五
<lb n="0870a25" ed="T"/>百<app type="star" corresp="#0869015"><lem wit="【大】">女除饉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">除饉女</rdg></app>皆已滅度。」梵志理家聞阿難言，靡
<lb n="0870a26" ed="T"/>不<app type="star" corresp="#0870003"><lem wit="【大】">擗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">躃</rdg></app>地椎心<note n="0870008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搣＝滅【三】</note><note n="0870008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搣【大】，滅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870008"><lem wit="【大】">搣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">滅</rdg></app>髮宛轉哀號云：「當奈何？吾
<lb n="0870a27" ed="T"/>等孤露將<note n="0870a2701" resp="CBETA" type="add">復【CB】【麗-CB】，腹【大】</note><app n="0870a2701"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">復<note type="cf1">K19n0753_p0723a19</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">腹</rdg></app>誰恃乎？」阿難又說：「三界是幻都
<lb n="0870a28" ed="T"/>為非常，身為苦器<app type="star" corresp="#0869040"><lem wit="【大】">𤺙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惱</rdg></app>痛所聚，唯泥<app type="star" corresp="#0869022"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洹</rdg></app>安，故三
<lb n="0870a29" ed="T"/>尊歸之也。」理家心解稽首足下。阿難還至佛
<pb n="0870b" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0145.0870b"/>
<lb n="0870b01" ed="T"/>所，如事以聞。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0870b0106" rend="inline">梵志理家即具葬具，馳詣精舍。
<lb n="0870b02" ed="T"/>時園門閉，理家使人緣入開門欲入講堂。有
<lb n="0870b03" ed="T"/>女沙彌<note n="0870009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝六【宋】</note><note n="0870009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，六【宋】</note><app n="0870009"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">六</rdg></app>人，一人得不還道，次者頻來，小
<lb n="0870b04" ed="T"/>者溝港，告理家曰：「吾師坐禪今得寂定，慎無
<lb n="0870b05" ed="T"/>擾也。」答曰：「師已滅度，不為定也。」沙彌聞之，
<lb n="0870b06" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0870003"><lem wit="【大】">擗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">躃</rdg></app>身絕息有頃乃<note n="0870010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穌＝蘇【三】</note><note n="0870010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穌【大】，蘇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870010"><lem wit="【大】">穌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">蘇</rdg></app>，哀號而曰：「誰當復誨
<lb n="0870b07" ed="T"/>吾等聖訓<note n="0870011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＋（矣）【三】</note><note n="0870011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕【大】，絕矣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870011"><lem wit="【大】">絕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">絕矣</rdg></app>吾者廢也？」理家覩之莫不舉哀，
<lb n="0870b08" ed="T"/>哀畢告沙彌曰：「佛本說經，恩愛雖會終必有
<lb n="0870b09" ed="T"/>離，世榮難保唯道可久，但當建志進取應真，
<lb n="0870b10" ed="T"/>滅三界苦。捐俗哀心也。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0870b1010" rend="inline">理家闍維畢，奉舍利
<lb n="0870b11" ed="T"/>詣佛所，佛告<app type="star" corresp="#0869018"><lem wit="【大】">鶖鷺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">秋露</rdg></app>子：「汝東向叉手下右膝
<lb n="0870b12" ed="T"/>曰：『有直信直業三神六智道神已足者，皆來
<lb n="0870b13" ed="T"/>赴斯。所以然者？佛母逮諸<anchor xml:id="fxT02p0870b03"/>除饉女五百人，今
<lb n="0870b14" ed="T"/>皆善逝，宜當<note n="0870012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（法）＋會【三】</note><note n="0870012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會【大】，法會【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870012"><lem wit="【大】">會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">法會</rdg></app>。』四方俱然。」於是四方各二百
<lb n="0870b15" ed="T"/>五十應真，神足飛來稽首佛足。佛起至大愛
<lb n="0870b16" ed="T"/>道舍利所，千比丘從，皆就。<note n="0870013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（座佛）＋告【三】</note><note n="0870013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告【大】，座佛告【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870013"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">座佛告</rdg></app>阿難：「取舍利盛
<lb n="0870b17" ed="T"/>之，以鉢著吾手中。」阿難如命，以鉢盛舍利長
<lb n="0870b18" ed="T"/>跪授佛，佛以兩手受之，告諸比丘：「斯聚舍利，
<lb n="0870b19" ed="T"/>本是穢身凶愚急暴，輕心疾轉嫉<note n="0870014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姤＝妬【三】</note><note n="0870014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姤【大】，妬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870014"><lem wit="【大】">姤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">妬</rdg></app>陰謀，敗
<lb n="0870b20" ed="T"/>道壞德為亂作先之類，今母拔女人兇愚之
<lb n="0870b21" ed="T"/>穢，為丈夫行獲應真道，<note n="0870015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔還〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0870015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870015"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>靈本無淨過虛
<lb n="0870b22" ed="T"/>空，行高<note n="0870016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（盡）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0870016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，無盡【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870016"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">無盡</rdg></app>蓋何其健哉！」佛告諸比丘及理家
<lb n="0870b23" ed="T"/>眾：「共為母及諸應真女興廟。」僉曰：「唯然！」於是
<lb n="0870b24" ed="T"/>天人鬼龍興廟立<note n="0870017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剎＝表【三】</note><note n="0870017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剎【大】，表【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870017"><lem wit="【大】">剎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">表</rdg></app>，華香作樂繞廟三匝。哀
<lb n="0870b25" ed="T"/><note n="0870018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝音【三】</note><note n="0870018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，音【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0870018"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">音</rdg></app>震國，詣佛敬信，輒說：「生死為苦，三界無安。」
<lb n="0870b26" ed="T"/>以釋來者，莫不歡喜，稽首而去。</p>
<lb n="0870b27" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛母般泥洹<note n="0870019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0870019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經一卷【宋】【元】</note><app n="0870019"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0870b28" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><head><note n="0870020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此記無於麗依宋元明載</note>佛般泥洹後變記</head>
<lb n="0870b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0870b2901">我般泥洹後百歲，我諸弟子沙門，聰明智
<pb n="0870c" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0145.0870c"/>
<lb n="0870c01" ed="T"/>慧如我無異。我般泥洹後二百歲時，阿育
<lb n="0870c02" ed="T"/>王從八王索八斛四斗舍利，一日中作八
<lb n="0870c03" ed="T"/>萬四千佛圖。三百歲時，若有出家作沙門，
<lb n="0870c04" ed="T"/>一日中便得道。四百歲時，數念佛及法以
<lb n="0870c05" ed="T"/>比丘僧，供養和<note n="0870021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝尚【明】</note><note n="0870021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，尚【明】</note><app n="0870021"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">尚</rdg></app>阿闍梨。五百歲時，沙
<lb n="0870c06" ed="T"/>門婆羅門及人民，無不啼泣念佛者。六百
<lb n="0870c07" ed="T"/>歲時，諸沙門便行入山中樹下塚間求道。
<lb n="0870c08" ed="T"/>七百歲時，便行內外學經，若有沙門婆羅
<lb n="0870c09" ed="T"/>門問事無不解了，悉壞九十六種外道。八
<lb n="0870c10" ed="T"/>百歲時，便復念行作佛圖<note n="0870022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">䔺＝<g ref="#CB01819"/>【元】【明】</note><note n="0870022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">䔺【大】，<g ref="#CB01819"/>【元】【明】</note><app n="0870022"><lem wit="【大】">䔺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><g ref="#CB01819"/></rdg></app>疾次作佛圖。
<lb n="0870c11" ed="T"/>九百歲時，便念行治生求利害處所。千歲
<lb n="0870c12" ed="T"/>時，便行與國王相隨教習兵法戰陣，自行
<lb n="0870c13" ed="T"/>屠殺妻娶婦女。</p>
<lb n="0870c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0870c1401">佛般泥洹後變記</p></cb:div>
